<h2><a name="y2011">year 2011</a></h2>

<p>
23. <strong>Fantoni R.</strong>, Giacometti A., Sciortino F., and Pastore G., <a target="_blank" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1039/C0SM00995D">Soft Matter <strong>7</strong>, 2419 (2011)</a>, (*) <br>
